'''Doria Achour''' (wavutse ku ya 1 Werurwe 1991) ni umukinnyi ndetse n'umuyobozi wa firimi mu Bufaransa ariko akomoka muri Tuniziya

== Ubuzima bwe ==
Achour ni umukobwa wumuyobozi wa firime wa tuniziya akaba n'umukinnyi wa filime Lotfi Achour na nyina w’Uburusiya akaba umwanditsi w'amakinamico. Mukuru we ni umwanditsi w'amakinamico, kandi afite murumuna we. Achour yakuriye mu cyiciro cya 12 cya Paris mu kirere cyari "icyerekezo cy'ubuhanzi, ariko ntabwo ari burugumesitiri." <ref name="LM2015">https://www.lemonde.fr/afrique/article/2015/06/19/doria-achour-un-travelling-entre-paris-et-tunis_4658141_3212.html</ref> Akiri umwana, yaherekeje ababyeyi be mu myitozo yabo no mu bitaramo byabo. <ref name="voici">http://www.voici.fr/bios-people/doria-achour</ref>

Mu 2002, Achour yerekanye umukobwa wa Sergi López muri ''Les Femmes... ou les enfants d'abord... [ fr ]'', iyobowe na Manuel Poirier . Nyina yamufashije kubona uruhare, abona itangazo muri ''Libération'' . Nyuma yuruhare rwe rwa mbere, Achor yafashe amasomo yo gukina umwaka umwe muri Théâtre des Déchargeurs. Yagize uruhare rwa kabiri muri firime nkeya, nka ''L'enemi naturel'' na ''L'École pour tous'' . <ref name="Express2014">http://www.lexpress.fr/culture/cinema/doria-achour-la-revelation-de-papa-was-not-a-rolling-stone_1603532.html</ref> Kugira ngo yibanze ku myigire ye, Achour yahagaritse umwuga we wa firime imyaka myinshi.  Achour yabonye impamyabumenyi y’ubuvanganzo yakuye muri kaminuza ya Paris-Sorbonne nyuma aza kubona impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri sinema yakuye muri kaminuza ya Paris Diderot . <ref name="LM2015" />

Muri 2012, Achour yakinnye umusore Yasmeen muri ''La fille publique'', kandi imico ye yahumekewe nubuzima bwa mbere bwa Cheyenne Carron . Mu mwaka wa 2013, Achour yayoboye filime ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Laisse-moi finir'', ku ngingo y'ubuzima muri Tuniziya nyuma y'Isoko ry'Abarabu igihe abayisilamu bigaruriraga.  Yerekanwe mu minsi mikuru myinshi kandi ihabwa igihembo cya Audience muri Made in Med marushanwa ya firime ngufi yo muri Kamena 2014. Imyitwarire ye muri ''La fille publique yakuruye'' umuyobozi Sylvie Ohayon, wakinnye uyu mukinnyi ukiri muto nka Stephanie muri film ya''Papa Was Not a Rolling Ston'' . Muri 2016, Achour yakinnye muri filime ye ya mbere yicyarabu, ''Yaka Ibyiringiro'' .  Yayoboye filime ngufi ''Le reste est l'œuvre de l'homme'', yatsindiye igihembo cya Jury mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2017. <ref>https://mediakwest.com/le-reste-est-l-oeuvre-de-l-homme-prix-du-jury-du-concours-sundance-tv/</ref> Yakinnye na Leila, umukobwa wabuze, muri Naidra Ayadi ya film ya ''Ma fille ya'' 2018. <ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/ma-fille-review-1147414</ref>

Achur ni agnostic.  Ni umukunzi wibitabo byo hagati. <ref>https://cheekmagazine.fr/les-yeux-dans-les-yeux/doria-achour/</ref>

